maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Henry
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Henry

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: I d-d-don't have any probes left, but I g-g-guess you know how they look.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Il ne m-m-me reste plus de s-sonde, mais je p-p-pense que tu sais à q-q-quoi elles ressemblent.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: I wonder if she'll turn up again...
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Je me demande si elle va encore se montrer...

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Henry
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Henry

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: I-I-It's you!
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: C-C-C'est toi !

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Hi!
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Salut !

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: At t-this point, someone might t-think you're stalking me.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: On p-p-pourrait presque se dire q-q-que tu me s-s-surveilles.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: It has been a while! And a-a-as usual you came at the right moment.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Cela fait un b-b-bail ! Et c-c-comme d'habitude, t-tu tombes à p-point nommé.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Another player has just p-placed a probe somewhere in t-t-t-this jungle.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Un autre j-j-joueur vient de p-p-placer une sonde quelque part dans c-c-cette jungle.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Even though I had some problems earlier.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Bien que j'aie eu quelques c-c-complications auparavant.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: D-D-Don't worry about it... It was just a misunderstanding.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Ne t-t-t'inquiète pas... C'était j-j-juste un malentendu.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: It j-j-just means I don't have much t-t-time left.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: ç-ça veut juste dire qu'il m-m-me reste plus beaucoup de t-t-temps.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: S-So would you be willing to help me survey this area too?
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: D-Donc est-ce que tu veux m'aider à é-étudier cette région ?

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: T-Thank you! T-this will be the last time, I p-p-promise.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: M-Merci ! C-Ce sera la dernière fois, p-p-promis.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: I d-d-don't have any probes left, but I g-g-guess you know what they look like by now.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Il ne m-m-me reste plus de s-sonde, mais je p-p-pense que tu sais à q-q-quoi elles ressemblent.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: O-Oh... You are not interested...
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: O-Oh... Tu n'es p-p-pas intéressée...

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Baxton
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Baxton

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Lady Lea!
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Mademoiselle Lea !
Salut... !

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: It seems we meet yet again. It must be fate.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: On se rencontre à nouveau. Cela doit être le destin.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Reports in this area have been made by dutiful players that a strange player was seen here.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Des signalements de joueurs consciencieux indiquent qu'ils ont vu un joueur étrange dans cette zone.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: One that appears as a humble NPC seeking help from other players.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Un qui se fait passer pour un humble PNJ demandant de l'aide d'autres joueurs.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Let me ask quite bluntly here Lady Lea...
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Laissez-moi vous demander très franchement, mademoiselle Lea...

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Did you accept a quest from an NPC by the name of... let me see here... \.\.\. \c[3]Henry\c[0]?
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Est-ce que vous avez accepté une quête d'un PNJ du nom de... laissez-moi voir...\.\.\. \c[3]Henry\c[0] ?

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Well this is quite unsettling. You are the third person to report so.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Bon cela devient assez inquiétant. Vous êtes la troisième personne à le signaler.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: I fear we have a person with malicious intent here.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Je crains que nous ayons à faire à une personne malintentionnée.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Ah, fear not Lady Lea. I do not believe you are involved in such shady business.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Ah, Mademoiselle Lea. Je sais que vous n'êtes pas délibérément impliquée là-dedans.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: I must however follow procedure and file a report against this player.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Je dois par contre suivre la procédure et écrire un procès verbal pour ce joueur.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Even if it is highly probable that \c[3]Henry\c[0] is just a cover name.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Même si c'est hautement probable que \c[3]Henry\c[0] n'est qu'un pseudonyme qu'il s'est donné.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: For now, I will manually complete the quest that has been given to you.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Pour l'instant, je vais manuellement terminer la quête qu'il vous a donnée.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: I am following a lead that will take me all the way to \c[3]\v[area.forest.name]\c[0].
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Je suis en train de suivre une piste qui va jusqu'à là \c[3]\v[area.forest.name]\c[0].

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: May we meet again under more pleasant circumstances next time, Lady Lea. Goodbye!
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Puissions-nous nous rencontrer en de plus plaisantes circonstances, Mademoiselle Lea. Au revoir !

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Bye...
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Bye...

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: So... a city in the middle of the Jungle?
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Donc... une ville en plein milieu de la Jungle ?

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Yes, and a giant of a city at that!
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Oui, et elle est gigantesque !

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: In the jungle?
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Dans la jungle ?

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Indeed! Human ingenuity shaped this hotspot of civilization amid this hostile environment!
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Exactement ! Une merveille de la civilisation humaine se trouve au sein de cette nature sauvage !

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: I can't wait to see it.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Je suis impatient de voir ça.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Back in the jungle!
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: De retour dans la jungle !

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: By the way, Lea.\. One thing I was wondering about...
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: D'ailleurs, Lea.\. Un truc que je me demandais...

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Back when you explored the jungle together with Grasshead.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: À l'époque, quand tu explorais la jungle avec Monsieur Tête-d'Herbe.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: ...\. How often did you lose sight of him?
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: ...\. Combien de fois tu l'as perdu de vue ?

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: What do you mean?
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Qu'est-ce que tu veux dire ?

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Just look at your hair!
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Regarde un peu tes cheveux !

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: It blends perfectly with the grass and plants of this place.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Ils se fondent parfaitement dans l'herbe et la verdure du coin.

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: This is nonsense!
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Quelles sottises !

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Ah oui?
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Ah oui ?

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: So?\. How often, Lea?
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Donc ?\. Combien de fois, Lea ?

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig: Oh, you have got to be kidding me!!
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text: Oh, tu te moques de moi !!

maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.orig:
I lied to her to keep her going.\.
Protecting her from the truth.\.
\.
Yet over time I noticed this...\.
growing feeling of guilt.
maps/jungle/path-02-crossroads.json/enti.text:
Je lui ai menti, pour qu'elle continue.\.
Pour la protéger de la vérité.\.
\.
Mais avec le temps, j'ai remarqué ce...\.
sentiment de honte qui grandissait en moi.
